# Repository .gitignore for gitignores-files Template Collection
#
# This file ignores development artifacts, editor files, and temporary files
# for this template repository. It is NOT a template file itself.
#
# The templates in subdirectories (languages/, frameworks/, tools/, etc.) are
# example .gitignore patterns for users to include in their own projects.

# ============================================================================
# REPOSITORY-SPECIFIC PATTERNS
# ============================================================================
# These patterns are specific to this repository's development and maintenance.
# They should NOT be included in user projects' .gitignore files.

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Operating System Files
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
